<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../731/1206731.xml">
Big River</link></musical>
</it>. More notably he starred opposite <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../394/18887394.xml">
John Hill</link> in the 2004 <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../127/89127.xml">
off-Broadway</link> hit <it><link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../878/17507878.xml">
Bare, a Pop Opera</link></it>. In Summer 2005, Michael played Nick, a sexually promiscuous gay man in love with a shark, in <physical_entity wordnetid="100001930" confidence="0.8">
